[{"id":985699,"node":"生活","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/life","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785","description":"<p>之前是洗澡之后就顺手把内裤手洗了，但是时间长了以后就觉得很麻烦，哪怕只要一两分钟的时间但是每天都要重复这个过程就觉得这两分钟时间都不想动。盆里已经堆了几条没洗的内裤了，看了一点没有想碰的欲望。最近一直在看内衣洗衣机，那种仿手洗的要好几千，便宜的几十的看起来操作很麻烦，而且担心洗不干净😓。好纠结，还是太懒惹的祸😅</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/985699","replies":161,"created_ts":1698308589,"created":"16:23:09","title":"不想洗内裤怎么办，觉得好麻烦","author":"KOMA1NIUJUNSHENG","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/KOMA1NIUJUNSHENG","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/966a8110199e8fb1bb6a61819724a6ee?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":985800,"node":"iPhone","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/iphone","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_mini.png?m=1630643991","description":"身边有个米家结晶粉，天天拿着个红米，跟我比配置、比价格。每次和他说手机这些都很烦，但又破解不了他的米氏对比法。例如小米 14 8+256 才 3999 ，iPhone 15Pro 8999,iPhone 有的小米都有","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/985800","replies":116,"created_ts":1698330745,"created":"22:32:25","title":"如何破解米式对比法","author":"ji76289","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/ji76289","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c575360da623e843f03a7c4a21e0ec35?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":985483,"node":"优惠信息","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/deals","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/8d31/7bdc/747_mini.png?m=1523201604","description":"<p><a href=\"https://v.115.com/1115?t1\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://v.115.com/1115?t1</a></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/985483","replies":112,"created_ts":1698275627,"created":"07:13:47","title":"115 会员 500 元 8 年","author":"IsaacYoung","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/IsaacYoung","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2d1d334c99ac05d44890bacbf6ad5b08?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":985613,"node":"小米","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/xiaomi","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/301a/d0e3/834_mini.png?m=1584400459","description":"<p>参考极客湾的视频： <a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1me411R7Ha\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1me411R7Ha</a></p>\n<p>虽然小米 14 今晚才开发布会，但视频已经出了，8Gen3 这次稳定发挥，成绩非常亮眼：CPU 单核成绩相比 A17 Pro 还有点差距，但多核成绩已经超越了 A17 Pro\n<img alt=\"CPU\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/g9O74j9.png\"/></p>\n<p>并且 CPU 多核负载的能耗也要强于 A17 Pro ，相比 8Gen2 也有不少的提升\n<img alt=\"CPU2\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HEUsiBp.png\"/></p>\n<p>同样的，在 GPU 上，8Gen3 的性能比苹果 A17 Pro 高 5%，但功耗只有 A17 Pro 的 75%，属实是赢麻了\n<img alt=\"GPU\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VW11W7a.png\"/></p>\n<p>GPU 的能耗方面也是目前移动端最强，尤其是高负载情况下，遥遥领先 A17 Pro\n<img alt=\"GPU2\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/raAgUEu.png\"/></p>\n<p>配合小米 14 可以看到 8Gen3 的 GPU 压力测试：性能接近当年笔记本上的 GTX 1050 ，并且稳定度达到了 89.6%，远高于 iPhone 15 Pro 上搭载的 A17 Pro\n<img alt=\"GPU3\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Gfufjks.png\"/></p>\n<p>光追性能方面：性能比 A17 Pro 高 14%，但功耗只有 A17 Pro 的 76%\n<img alt=\"GPU4\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gYQCvZJ.png\"/></p>\n<p>最后是传统项目，30 分钟原神机身温度测试，小米 14 是 45.4 度，而 iPhone 15 Pro 来到了 46.9 度\n<img alt=\"ALL\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/j0Ap8XN.png\"/></p>\n<p>还有一个值得关注的点是，8Gen3 彻底抛弃了 32 位的支持，仅支持 64 位应用，考虑到这次芯片很给力，安卓厂商应该都会上搭载 8Gen3 的新机，因此会推动某些顽固应用转向 64 位</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/985613","replies":110,"created_ts":1698294492,"created":"12:28:12","title":"小米 14 / 骁龙 8Gen3 发布了","author":"charlieethan","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/charlieethan","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1df7/b506/422562_mini.png?m=1649775176"},{"id":985489,"node":"游戏","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/games","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b53b/3a3d/55_mini.png?m=1611920927","description":"<p>可以对战聊天，钻石管够，vps 带宽很小，入服人数有限</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/985489","replies":108,"created_ts":1698279923,"created":"08:25:23","title":"部落冲突公益养老服有人玩么","author":"Xiangliangliang","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Xiangliangliang","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5c8c5babeb296b2eeb5f0540fda5c968?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":985488,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"双 11 ，准备买个 65 寸的电视，预算 5k ，但是选择好像很少，备选了海信 65E8H 和小米 S Pro miniLED ，价格分别是 4999 和 4699 ，配置小米这个要更好点，但是不太清楚小米可靠性怎么样？其他暂时这个预算没看到合适的，大佬们有推荐的吗？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/985488","replies":102,"created_ts":1698279856,"created":"08:24:16","title":"预算 5k 推荐下电视","author":"eggt","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/eggt","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/8b37a1be671cf3f1671c3a6142f8fc2d?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":985690,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"目前的话费是 0 元 。<br /><br />联通中国通 0 元<br />电信  公司宽带的号码 0 元<br /><br />然后想上一个 马来 的紫卡，99RM ， 算下来要 160 块一个月<br /><br />感觉好伤啊","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/985690","replies":100,"created_ts":1698308120,"created":"16:15:20","title":"大家的手机月话费是多少啊？","author":"yiyiwa","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/yiyiwa","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1369/2b5b/113488_mini.png?m=1430017574"},{"id":985680,"node":"职场话题","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/career","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1695370146","description":"<p>背景：我的工作是做 SAAS 系统项目的，销售卖出去一个系统+交付服务，我是项目负责人兼交付实施，但是已经交付很长时间了，有非常多的需求不能满足客户需求，公司也确定不会开发也无法推进，客户忍无可忍决定更换系统，但他没告诉我</p>\n<p>然后昨天客户喊我过去见面，我去了，客户把新的供应商（我们的竞争对手）也叫来了，让我给这个新的供应商逐一讲解我们系统逻辑，还要配合竞对帮客户把数据迁移到对方的系统里。无法拒绝，因为还在合同期内。</p>\n<p>这感觉就像 隔壁老王睡了我老婆，然后还要让我帮他戴套一样难受——好在我没有老婆</p>\n<p>其实这就是公司给我的烫手项目，我完全可以摆烂，但是其他人都不敢出来面对客户，我一直顶着大半年。也准备跑路了，根本没法干，销售签约一通瞎吹，开发一问这也不开发那也不能实现，客户要退款或者不续费，那就给我扣上一顶“没有合理控制客户预期的”帽子</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/985680","replies":99,"created_ts":1698306110,"created":"15:41:50","title":"经历了有史以来工作中最大的奇耻大辱","author":"ODESZA","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/ODESZA","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3c0b/7be8/466174_mini.png?m=1605682853"},{"id":985571,"node":"分享发现","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/share","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_mini.png?m=1650127281","description":"<p>来源：<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1me411R7Ha/?spm_id_from=333.337.search-card.all.click&amp;vd_source=3f22c0cbc5734cd4b5d6e8850ae61897\" rel=\"nofollow\">小米 14 性能分析：骁龙 8Gen3 到底有多强？</a></p>\n<p>省流：单核打不过 Apple ，GPU 大幅度领先 A17 Pro</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/985571","replies":94,"created_ts":1698289159,"created":"10:59:19","title":"看了下极客湾的 8Gen3 测评，感觉苹果在 SOC 的优势正在缩小","author":"Morii","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Morii","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6814/f790/549564_mini.png?m=1683338509"},{"id":985602,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"摸鱼看以色列的新闻想起来犹太教和基督教，然后联想到国内的宗教。<br />  国内宗教第一反应肯定是儒释道，佛教道教的信仰元素在日常很容易见到，但是想起来儒教就有些模糊，在古代除了搞搞祭祀，古代读书人算教徒？四书五经算教义？  信这个教的话供的应该是孔子吧，但是感觉也没什么实际的精神传承之类的。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/985602","replies":88,"created_ts":1698291804,"created":"11:43:24","title":"儒教到底是什么","author":"karatsuba","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/karatsuba","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f53d/1ea5/516315_mini.png?m=1690358993"},{"id":985774,"node":"北京","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/beijing","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1f0e/3dad/19_mini.png?m=1650127314","description":"<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferr